- <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/feature/goddard/2022/mars-ocean"> NASA-Funded Study Extends Period When Mars Could Have Supported Life </a> (NASA HQ)<br>
- <a href="https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/model-suggests-toxic-transformation-on-venus/"> Model Suggests Toxic Transformation on Venus </a> (Scientific American)<br>
